---
// Video Section based on crawled 10botics.com data
// This was originally Elementor video widgets
---

<section class="py-16 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
        課程介紹影片
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        透過影片了解我們的課程內容和教學方式
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Video 1 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
        <div class="aspect-w-16 aspect-h-9 bg-gray-200 relative">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-red-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center cursor-pointer hover:bg-red-700 transition-colors">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M8 5v14l11-7z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-4 bg-black bg-opacity-75 text-white px-3 py-1 rounded text-sm">
            課程介紹
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">STEM 課程概覽</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
            了解我們的 STEM 課程如何幫助學生發展創新思維和解決問題的能力。
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Video 2 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
        <div class="aspect-w-16 aspect-h-9 bg-gray-200 relative">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-red-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center cursor-pointer hover:bg-red-700 transition-colors">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M8 5v14l11-7z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-4 bg-black bg-opacity-75 text-white px-3 py-1 rounded text-sm">
            學生作品
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">學生作品展示</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
            看看學生們在課程中創作的精彩作品，展現他們的創意和學習成果。
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Video 3 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
        <div class="aspect-w-16 aspect-h-9 bg-gray-200 relative">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-red-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center cursor-pointer hover:bg-red-700 transition-colors">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M8 5v14l11-7z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-4 bg-black bg-opacity-75 text-white px-3 py-1 rounded text-sm">
            比賽活動
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">比賽活動回顧</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
            回顧我們舉辦的各種 STEM 比賽活動，看看學生們如何在競賽中成長。
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- About Section -->
    <div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
          關於 10Botics
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
          10Botics 是香港科學園初創公司，過去與 50 多間學校和教育機構合作。我們的使命是利用人工智能知識為下一代做好準備，並專注於 STEM 課程的研發及教學，使孩子們可以更容易地學習人工智能（AI）。
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">
          我們的學習工具及課程是由專業 STEM 團隊共同開發，旨在使孩子、老師和父母可以通過現實生活的例子中學習到課程複雜、深奧的概念，令學習變得輕鬆及有趣。
        </p>
        <a href="/about" class="bg-blue-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">
          了解更多
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gray-200 rounded-lg h-64 flex items-center justify-center">
        <span class="text-gray-600">公司介紹圖片</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 